  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV43">
<l>kaṇṇuñcen tāmarai kaiyum mavaiyaṭi yōvavaiyē</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṅ kariyatōr mālvarai pōṉṟu mativikaṟpāl</l>
<l>viṇṇuṅ kaṭantumpa rappāṉmik kumaṟṟep pālevarkku</l>
<l>meṇṇu miṭattatu vōvempi rāṉa teḻiṉiṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[His] eyes red lotus, [his] hands too such, as for [his] feet, they are similar.</l>
<l>[His] colour that is black resembles a huge mountain. By a diversity of minds,</l>
<l>increasing in that place beyond after [his] crossing the sky, or in any place for anyone,</l>
<l>as for that, when one contemplates it, is the beautiful colour of our lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
